{
  "chapter": "053",
  "title": "萧相国世家",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：萧何\">萧相国何（萧何）</span>，是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>郡<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">丰</span>邑人。因通晓文法无所枉害，担任<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>县<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">主吏掾</span>。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>还是<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">布</span>衣平民时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：萧何\">何（萧何）</span>多次凭借吏员身份维护<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">亭长</span>时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：萧何\">何（萧何）</span>常常从旁辅助他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>作为吏员服役前往<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">咸阳</span>，官吏们送行都奉上<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">钱</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三</span>百，唯独<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：萧何\">何（萧何）</span>送了<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五</span>百。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "秦朝<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史</span>巡察郡县的和郡守的从事，常常明察事务。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：萧何\">何（萧何）</span>于是得以处理<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">泗水</span>郡<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">卒史</span>的事务，考核第一。秦<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史</span>想入朝奏请征召<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：萧何\">何（萧何）</span>入京，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：萧何\">何（萧何）</span>坚决辞谢，才没有前往。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "等到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>起事做了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：萧何\">何（萧何）</span>经常担任县丞督办事务。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公到达<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">咸阳</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸将</span>都争着跑到存放<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">帛</span>财物的府库去瓜分，唯独<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：萧何\">何（萧何）</span>先进入收取秦<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史</span>所掌的律<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">令</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">图书</span>收藏起来。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>公做了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>，任用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：萧何\">何（萧何）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项王</span>与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">屠</span>戮焚烧<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">咸阳</span>而离去。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>之所以能详知<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>的险要关塞、户口多少、强弱所在、百姓疾苦，正是因为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：萧何\">何（萧何）</span>全部得到了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">图书</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：萧何\">何（萧何）</span>又进言推荐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韩信</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>任用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩信\">信（韩信）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大将军</span>。此事记载在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩信\">淮阴侯（韩信）</span>的事迹之中。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>率领<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>东进平定三<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：萧何\">何（萧何）</span>以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>身份留守收抚<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">巴</span>蜀，安抚晓谕百姓，供给军粮。汉<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：萧何\">何（萧何）</span>留守<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关中</span>，侍奉<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>，治理<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">栎阳</span>。制定<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>令制度，建立<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">宗庙</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">社稷</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">宫室</span>县邑，总是先上奏，获准后才照办；来不及奏报的，就根据情势便宜行事，等<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>回来再汇报。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关中</span>事务计算户口转运漕粮供给军队，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>多次损失军队逃离，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：萧何\">何（萧何）</span>常在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关中</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">征发</span>兵员，随时补充缺额。皇上因此专门把<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关中</span>事务托付给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：萧何\">何（萧何）</span>。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "汉<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">京索</span>一带对峙，皇上多次派使者慰劳<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鲍生</span>对<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：汉王\">王（汉王）</span>暴晒<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">衣</span>服、露宿野外，却多次派使者慰劳您，这是对您有疑心啊。为您打算，不如派您的子孙兄弟中能拿<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>器的人全部到军营去，皇上必定更信任您。\"于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：萧何\">何（萧何）</span>听从他的计策，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>大为高兴。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "汉<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五年</span>，已经<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span>，平定<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>，按功行封。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>争功，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">一年多</span>也未能定下来。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>认为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">萧何</span>功劳最大，封为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">酂侯</span>，所<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">食</span>邑最多。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">功臣</span>们都说：\"我们身披坚甲、手执利刃，多的打过<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百馀</span>仗，少的也经历<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数十</span>次战斗，攻〖◈攻城略地，功劳大小各有差等。如今<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">萧何</span>未曾有过汗<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>功劳，只凭文墨议论，不曾作战，反而位居我们之上，这是为什么？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸君</span>懂得打猎吗？\"回答说：\"懂得。\"又问：\"懂得猎<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">狗</span>吗？\"回答说：\"懂得。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>说：\"打猎时，追击<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>死<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">兽</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">兔</span>的是<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">狗</span>，而发纵指示<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">兽</span>之所在的是人。如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸君</span>只能捕到逃跑的<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">兽</span>罢了，功劳就像<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">狗</span>。至于<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">萧何</span>，发纵指示，功劳就像人。何况<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸君</span>只是只身跟随我，多者不过<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">两三人</span>。如今<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">萧何</span>全家族<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数十人</span>都跟随我，这功劳不可忘啊。\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>都不敢再说话。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span>都已受封完毕，到奏议位次时，都说：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">平阳侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹参</span>身受七十处伤，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>城略地，功劳最多，应当排第一。\"皇上已经委屈了<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">功臣</span>，多<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">萧何</span>，到议位次时无法再驳回，然而心中想让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：萧何\">何（萧何）</span>排第一。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">关内侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鄂君</span>进言说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>的议论都错了。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹参</span>虽有野战攻地的功劳，这不过是一时之功。皇上与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>对峙五年，经常损失军队丢失众人，独自逃亡多次。然而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">萧何</span>常从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关中</span>派军补充缺口，并非皇上下诏<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">令</span>征召，却有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数万</span>之众屡次在皇上匮乏时赶到。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>相持几年，军中没有现存的粮食，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">萧何</span>从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关中</span>转运漕粮，供给不乏。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>虽然多次失掉<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">山东</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">萧何</span>却常保全<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关中</span>以待<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>，这是万世之功啊。如今即使失去<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹参</span>等上百人，对<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>又有何缺憾？<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>得到他们也不必依靠才保全。怎能用一时之功而凌驾万世之功呢！<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">萧何</span>当为第一，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹参</span>次之。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>说：\"好。\"于是下令<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">萧何</span>可以带<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">剑</span>穿<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">履</span>上殿，入朝不用小步疾行。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "皇上说：\"我听说举荐贤才的人当受上赏。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">萧何</span>功劳虽高，得到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鄂君</span>的举荐才更显彰明。\"于是因<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鄂君</span>原来所<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">食</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">关内侯</span>邑，改封为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">安平侯</span>。这一天，全部<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：萧何\">何（萧何）</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父子</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">兄弟</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十馀人</span>，都有食邑。又加<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：萧何\">何（萧何）</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二千户</span>，因为当年皇上作为吏员服役去<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">咸阳</span>时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：萧何\">何（萧何）</span>比别人多送我<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">钱</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二</span>百的缘故。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "汉<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十一年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈豨</span>谋反，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>亲自带兵，到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>。还没平定，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">淮阴侯</span>又在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关中</span>谋反，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕后</span>采用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">萧何</span>的计策，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">淮阴侯</span>，此事记载在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩信\">淮阴（韩信）</span>的事迹中。皇上听说<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">淮阴侯</span>被诛后，派使者<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">拜</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：萧何\">何（萧何）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>，加封<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五千户</span>，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">令</span>派卒<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五百人</span>和一名<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">都尉</span>担任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>的卫队。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸君</span>都来祝贺，唯独<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">召平</span>来吊唁。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">召平</span>是原来<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">东陵侯</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>被破后，他变为<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">布</span>衣，贫穷，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长安</span>城东种瓜，瓜很美味，所以世俗称为\"<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东陵</span>瓜\"，是从<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">召平</span>得名的。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">召平</span>对<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>说：\"祸患从此开始了。皇上在外暴晒露宿，而您守在朝中，未经矢石之险却给您加封设置卫队，是因为如今<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">淮阴侯</span>刚在京中谋反，对您起了疑心。设卫队来守护您，不是宠信您。希望您辞封不受，全部把家里私财拿出来助军，皇上就会高兴。\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>听从他的计策，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>于是大喜。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "汉<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十二年</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">秋</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黥布</span>谋反，皇上亲自带兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>讨他，多次派使者问<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：萧何\">何（萧何）</span>在做什么。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>因为皇上在军中，就亲自抚慰勉励<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>，把所有家财拿出来助军，和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈豨</span>时一样。有门客对<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>说：\"您<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">灭族</span>不远了。您身为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>，功劳第一，还能再加什么？而您当初进<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关中</span>，得到<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>之心，已十余年了，大家都归附您，您还孜孜不倦地取悦民心。皇上之所以多次问您在做什么，就是怕您在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关中</span>动摇他。如今您<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">何</span>不多买田地，以低价强买或赊借来玷污自己？皇上的心才会安。\"于是<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>听从他的计策，皇上于是大为高兴。"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "皇上讨伐<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">布</span>军回来，百姓拦路上书，说<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>贱买强买民田民宅<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数千万</span>。皇上回到京城，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>前来拜见。皇上笑着说：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>竟然这样利民！\"把百姓所上的书都给<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>，说：\"您自己去向百姓谢罪吧。\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>于是替百姓请求说：\"<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长安</span>地方狭小，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">上林</span>苑中多有空地，被废弃着，希望朝廷<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">令</span>允许百姓进去耕种，留下禾秆不收，用来喂<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">禽兽</span>。\"皇上大怒说：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>接受了许多商人的财物，竟替他们请我的苑囿！\"于是把<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>交给<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">廷尉</span>，戴上<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">械</span>具关押他。过了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">数天</span>，姓王的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">卫尉</span>侍立一旁，上前问道：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>有什么大罪，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>这么急着关押他？\"皇上说：\"我听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李斯</span>做<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">皇帝</span>的相国，有好事归于君主，有坏事自己承担。如今<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>多受商人的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span>钱而替百姓请求我的苑囿，来讨好百姓，所以把他关押治罪。\"王<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">卫尉</span>说：\"身为本职事务如果有利于民而为民请求，这正是<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">宰相</span>该做的事，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>怎能反而怀疑<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>接受商人的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">钱</span>财呢！况且<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>对峙数年，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈豨</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黥布</span>谋反，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>亲自带兵出征，那时候，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>留守<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关中</span>，只要动一动脚，函谷关以西就不是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>的了。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>不在那时谋取私利，如今反倒贪图商人的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span>钱吗？况且<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>因为不听说自己的过失而失去<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李斯</span>为君分担过失，又有什么值得效<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>的呢。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>怎么怀疑<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">宰相</span>这样浅薄啊。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>不高兴。当天，派使者持<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">节</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">赦</span>免放出<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>年老，向来恭敬谨慎，入朝，赤<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">跣</span>着脚谢罪。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>说：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>算了吧！<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>替百姓请苑，我不准许，我不过是个桀纣一样的君主，而<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>却是贤相。我故意关押<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>，是想让<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>听说我的过失。\""
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：萧何\">何（萧何）</span>向来与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹参</span>不和，等到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：萧何\">何（萧何）</span>病重，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝惠</span>亲自来探视<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>的病情，趁机问道：\"您百年之后，谁可以代替您？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：萧何\">何（萧何）</span>回答说：\"知道臣下的莫过于君主。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝惠</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹参</span>怎么样？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：萧何\">何（萧何）</span>叩头说：\"陛下得到合适的人选了！臣死而无憾了！\""
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：萧何\">何（萧何）</span>购置田宅一定选在偏僻之处，建造住宅不修筑高墙大屋。他说：\"后世子孙贤能，就效法我的俭朴；不贤能，也不会被权势之家夺走。\""
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝惠</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二年</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：萧何\">何（萧何）</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">卒</span>去世，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">谥</span>号为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">文终侯</span>。"
    },
    "16": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "他的后嗣因犯罪丢失<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">侯</span>爵的有四代，断绝封号，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>每次都再找<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：萧何\">何（萧何）</span>的后代，封续<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">酂侯</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">功臣</span>没有能与他相比的。"
    },
    "17": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：萧<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：萧何\">何（萧何）</span>在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>时做<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">刀笔</span>小吏，默默无闻没有奇特的节操。到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>兴起，依托<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">日月</span>般的光辉，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：萧何\">何（萧何）</span>谨守<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">管籥</span>钥匙，顺应百姓苦于秦<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>的形势，顺流而下与民更始。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩信\">淮阴（韩信）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黥布</span>等都以<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">诛灭</span>告终，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：萧何\">何（萧何）</span>的功勋却灿烂显赫。位居<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>之首，名声流传后世，可以与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">闳夭</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">散宜生</span>等人争辉了。"
    },
    "18": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">萧何</span>做吏员，通晓文法而无所枉害。 辅佐兴<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>，举族从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>起事。 守卫<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关中</span>，转输全靠他。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">军</span>屡次疲弱，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵</span>必与相会。 约<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>可以长久，收<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">图</span>籍可以宏大。 指示猎物发动猎手，功劳实为最高。 政令堪称划一，家居却不奢泰。 续绝宠赐勤勉，典礼表彰其<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">带</span>砺之盟。"
    }
  }
}